PR DESCRIPTION:
This follows the OpenTelemetry semantic conventions for servers: https://opentelemetry.io/docs/specs/semconv/gen-ai/mcp/#server

Is only compatible with Quarkus 3.33+
If OTel is disabled either at build or runtime, the tracing overhead should be minimal.
I probably over tested this... We might remove some of them, depending on the review.

